  <diagram name="4. Status" id="status">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1800" dy="1100" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1800" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="t4" value="Status &amp; What's Next" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;fontSize=22;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="20" width="1720" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t4s" value="What shipped, what's waiting on other people, what needs product decisions from you." style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;fontSize=13;align=center;fontColor=#555;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="62" width="1720" height="24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c1" value="✅ SHIPPED (origin/master, deployed, tested)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;opacity=80;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="110" width="560" height="900" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s1" value="&lt;b&gt;Security &amp; reliability&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;• Least-privilege permission model (6 narrow Graph perms)&#xa;• EnableUserLookup master gate&#xa;• 429 retry wrapper (3 retries, 30s cap)&#xa;• Consent revocation detection → audit event&#xa;• Sentinel labels include labelType:User&#xa;• Cross-RG workspace support" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="160" width="520" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s2" value="&lt;b&gt;Features&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;• 16 toggles documented &amp; wired&#xa;• Force MFA Re-registration (new, universal fallback)&#xa;• Data-ingest-only mode (ENABLE_USER_LOOKUP=false)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="390" width="520" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s3" value="&lt;b&gt;Operations &amp; distribution&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;• v1.1.0 GitHub release (auto-built via tag workflow)&#xa;• Deploy-to-Azure button working&#xa;• GitHub Actions CI on every PR/push&#xa;• Customer troubleshooting runbook (12 scenarios)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="550" width="520" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s4" value="&lt;b&gt;Quality&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;• 23 unit tests (mocked, CI-safe)&#xa;• Live integration test (test_actions.py, 13 cases)&#xa;• Code review pass clean (2 bugs found, both fixed)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="740" width="520" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s5" value="15 commits on master between 4dd0535 and b66a0b4" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;fontSize=11;align=center;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#2d7d32;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="900" width="520" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c2" value="⏸ BLOCKED ON ADMIN (external action)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;opacity=80;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="620" y="110" width="540" height="900" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b1" value="&lt;b&gt;1. Remove old User.ReadWrite.All grant from SP&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;The service principal still has an old broad grant from&#xa;before the least-privilege refactor. Our current login&#xa;cannot delete it (Authorization_RequestDenied).&#xa;&#xa;Needs: Privileged Role Admin or Global Admin to run&#xa;one az CLI command (documented in runbook).&#xa;&#xa;Until this clears, we can't prove that the narrow&#xa;permissions alone are sufficient — the broad grant&#xa;silently covers everything." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="640" y="160" width="500" height="280" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b2" value="&lt;b&gt;2. Grant Force MFA permission + role to SP&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;To run the live E2E test for the new Force MFA feature:&#xa;• Grant UserAuthenticationMethod.ReadWrite.All&#xa;  (application permission + admin consent)&#xa;• Assign Privileged Authentication Administrator role&#xa;  to the service principal&#xa;&#xa;Unit tests already pass (7/7 mock-based).&#xa;Live test without admin grant will return 403." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="640" y="460" width="500" height="270" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b3" value="&lt;b&gt;3. Incidents Content Hub PR review&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;PR #13628 open in Azure/Azure-Sentinel, MS reviewer&#xa;response pending for weeks. Not Entra-ID-specific but&#xa;blocks overall SOCRadar marketplace strategy." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="640" y="750" width="500" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c3" value="📋 NEEDS YOUR DECISION" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;opacity=80;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1180" y="110" width="580" height="900" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="d1" value="&lt;b&gt;Q1. Content Hub for Entra ID?&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Publish as official Sentinel marketplace solution&#xa;(like Incidents / Feeds / TAXII).&#xa;Effort: 2-3 sessions + Microsoft Partner Center review.&#xa;&#xa;Decision: yes (queue as Tier 3) / no (stay with ARM button)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1200" y="160" width="540" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="d2" value="&lt;b&gt;Q2. Kill the client secret (FIC migration)?&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Move from ENTRA_CLIENT_SECRET to Federated Identity&#xa;Credential (passwordless). Eliminates 2-year rotation clock.&#xa;Breaking for existing deployments.&#xa;&#xa;Decision: now (if no prod customers) / defer (phased migration)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1200" y="360" width="540" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="d3" value="&lt;b&gt;Q3. Add Programmatic Conditional Access (Option D)?&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Alternative to Force MFA re-registration: create a per-user&#xa;CA policy that requires MFA for X hours. Less destructive.&#xa;Requires P1/P2 (same as Confirm Risky).&#xa;&#xa;Decision: add (softer option for P1/P2 customers) / skip" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1200" y="560" width="540" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="d4" value="&lt;b&gt;Q4. When does MSSP multi-tenant ship?&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Design is done (consent-per-tenant, domain→tenant routing).&#xa;Implementation: 1-2 sessions + 2-tenant E2E test.&#xa;&#xa;Decision: build now (if MSSP customer pipeline exists) / defer (build when demand lands)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1200" y="760" width="540" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
